{"word":"παλλακεύομαι","slug":"παλλακεύομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παλλακεύομαι</b></el> <el>(παλλᾰκεύομαι,) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>as <a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, <el>π. τινα</el> <i>to keep as a concubine</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be a concubine</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>παλλᾰκή</el>\n"}]}